result.title: Codeforces Tags
result.content:
Hello,

I just found that it is possible to search with multiple tags in problemset. If you want to find problems with data structures and dp you can do this: http://codeforces.com/problemset/tags/data%20structures,dp and with binary search: http://codeforces.com/problemset/tags/data%20structures,dp,binary%20search You put comma between the tags
